<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٧٢⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٨٠٥٢ -<span class="c5"> عَنِ ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ قَالَ:</span> قُلْتُ لِعَطَاءٍ: <span class="c2">«الطَّبِيبُ يَبُطُّ الْجُرْحَ فَيَمُوتُ فِي يَدِهِ»</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«لَيْسَ عَلَيْهِ عَقْلٌ»</span> وَعَمْرُو بْنُ دِينَارٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>